---
title: Tomato Bisque with Cheesy Toasts and Balsamic Greens
description: We’re taking classic, comforting tomato soup and turning things up a notch, giving it a swirl of decadent sour cream and herby pesto. On the side, we’ve got a simple balsamic salad and melty gruyère cheese toasts—they’re so good you could eat ‘em on their own, but you’ll wanna dunk ‘em in the soup, then dunk ‘em again!
